Andrés González Jaén (amụrụ na 21 Mee 1993), nke a maara dị ka Zubi, bụ onye na-agba bọọlụ na Spain nke na-agba Cacereño dị ka onye na-eme egwuregwu n'aka ekpe.
A mụrụ Zubi na Cáceres, Extremadura
Ọ gbara bọọlụ ndị ntorobịa na Real Valladolid, na-eme nke mbụ ya dị ka onye okenye n'afọ 2012 na ndị na-echekwa na Tercera División
Na 30 October 2013 Zubi mere ìgwè mbụ ya - na La Liga - mpụta mbụ, na-egwu nkeji abụọ ikpeazụ na 2-2 n'ụlọ adọta megide Real Sociedad
Na 17 Julaị n'afọ sochiri ya, ọ kwagara n'òtù nchekwa ọzọ, Atlético Madrid B na Segunda División B.
